casebody.data:
Larry Eugene MANN, petitioner,
v.
FLORIDA. No. 12-9643 (12A968). Supreme Court of the United States April 10, 2013.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him referred to the Court denied. Motion of Mark Fondacaro, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Florida denied.
